{"hash":"b3c201724616bfa7aab137f6fc6bd393fafa31bc","data":{"doc":{"title":"Informe Allure","path":"/plugins/allure/","date":"3. June 2026","content":"<p>Un exportador que escribe los resultados de ejecución de Wakamiti en el formato esperado por Allure.</p>\n<p>La salida generada se puede consumir directamente con las herramientas CLI de Allure, por ejemplo con <code>allure serve</code>.</p>\n<hr>\n<ul id=\"toc\">\n<li><a href=\"#instalaci%C3%B3n\">Instalación</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#configuraci%C3%B3n\">Configuración</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#allurereportoutput\"><code>allureReport.output</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"instalación\"><a href=\"#instalaci%C3%B3n\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Instalación</h2>\n<p>Incluye el módulo en la sección correspondiente.</p>\n<div id=\"coord\" class=\"remark-code-tabs\"><label for=\"coord#0\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#0 name=\"coord\" checked/> yaml\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">es.iti.wakamiti:allure-wakamiti-plugin:1.0.0</code></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">es.iti.wakamiti:allure-wakamiti-plugin:1.0.0</pre></div></div><label for=\"coord#2\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#2 name=\"coord\" /> maven\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;dependency>\n  &lt;groupId>es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId>\n  &lt;artifactId>allure-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId>\n  &lt;version>1.0.0&lt;/version>\n&lt;/dependency></code></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n  &lt;groupId&gt;es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId&gt;\n  &lt;artifactId&gt;allure-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n  &lt;version&gt;1.0.0&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre></div></div></div>\n<hr class=\"remark-code-tabs-x\" rel=\"coord#maven\" />\n<h2 id=\"configuración\"><a href=\"#configuraci%C3%B3n\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Configuración</h2>\n<h3 id=\"allurereportoutput\"><a href=\"#allurereportoutput\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code>allureReport.output</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tipo: <code>file</code></li>\n<li>Por defecto: <code>allure-results</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>El directorio de salida donde se generan los ficheros Allure <code>*-result.json</code>.</p>\n<p>Ejemplo:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">allureReport</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> target/allure<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>results</code></pre></div>\n"}},"context":{"id":"56221a409bc4d2768e0c1dff3f7dadfd","path":"/plugins/allure/","locale":"es"}}